FBIS4-28993 "dreas115_n_94006" FBIS-EAS-94-115 Daily Report 14 Jun 1994 Vietnam Agreement on Education Signed With Australia Agreement on Education Signed With Australia BK1406064994 Melbourne Radio Australia in English 0500 GMT 14 Jun 94 BK1406064994 Melbourne Radio Australia English BFN [Text] Australia and Vietnam have signed an agreement on cooperation in education and training. The Vietnamese minister of education and training, Tran Hong Quan, and Australia's minister for employment and training, Simon Crean, signed the agreement in Hanoi. The agreement reinforces Australia's commitment to building closer trade and investment links with Vietnam. Mr. Crean is in Vietnam as part of the seven-day program promoting Australia's education and training expertise in Vietnam, Indonesia, and Malaysia.
